    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm sitting in front of the cliffs in etretat right now... it's beautiful, i guess. but honestly, i feel like i've checked every box on my itinerary. i've seen the sights, i've done the walks. i just feel like i've reached the part of the trip where there's nothing left to see. like i'm just waiting for the last train back home.",
